Implementation


The game is built using HTML for structure, CSS for futuristic neon design, and JavaScript for logic and interactivity.


Each player alternates turns until one wins or the game draws.


Scores are automatically updated and stored persistently in localStorage.


The design is fully responsive for mobile and desktop.


The project was deployed on Netlify for easy access.

